<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Why AI - Smart Farming Assistant</title>
    <link
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/tailwindcss/2.2.19/tailwind.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Arial", sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f4f9;
        color: #333;
      }
      .app-logo {
        width: 32px;
        height: 32px;
        stroke: currentColor;
      }
      .content-section {
        max-width: 1000px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem;
      }
      .benefit-list li {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
        position: relative;
      }
      .benefit-list li::before {
        content: "â€¢";
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        color: #4caf50;
      }
      .home-button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
        background-color: #4caf50;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 0.375rem;
        transition: background-color 0.2s;
      }
      .home-button:hover {
        background-color: #45a049;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="bg-green-600 text-white py-8">
      <div class="content-section">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-4">
          <svg
            class="app-logo"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
          >
            <path d="M12 19l9 2-9-18-9 18 9-2zm0 0v-8" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-2xl font-bold">Smart Farming App</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center">Why AI in Agriculture?</h1>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="py-12">
      <div class="content-section space-y-12">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">
            Transforming Farming Practices
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Artificial Intelligence is revolutionizing agriculture by providing
            farmers with powerful tools to enhance productivity and
            sustainability. Through advanced data analysis, farmers can now make
            more informed decisions based on real-time insights and historical
            patterns.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">
            Benefits of AI in Agriculture
          </h2>
          <ul class="benefit-list text-gray-700">
            <li>
              Improved crop yields through precision farming and optimized
              resource allocation
            </li>
            <li>
              Efficient water and resource management, significantly reducing
              waste and environmental impact
            </li>
            <li>
              Advanced predictive analytics for better planning and risk
              management strategies
            </li>
            <li>
              Enhanced pest and disease detection using AI-powered monitoring
              systems
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Conclusion</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            The integration of AI in agriculture represents a crucial step
            towards sustainable farming practices and improved food security. By
            embracing these innovative technologies, farmers can optimize their
            operations while contributing to environmental conservation.
          </p>
        </section>

        <div class="text-center mt-8">
          <a href="/" class="home-button"> Back to Home </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
